name: StrayaCraft
description:
After the 3rd world war and a long nuclear winter, the only continent where life could barely survive was Australia. A few generations later, what’s left of humanity has reached the stars. Play as the Australian Space Force and crush the Kiwi rebellion.

Fully Playable in browser. Textures/Lighting is a little better in the .exe version (to be uploaded later).

Ludum Dare Page: https://ldjam.com/events/ludum-dare/51/strayacraft
